ItemSizeByCell = Vector2i(5, 5)
ItemName = "Laptop"
ItemDescription = "Your trusty laptop and charger. You were lucky enough to be one of 20 students in your school to be given this by your school when you were 16. It runs slow, has a loud fan, and gave you so many opportunities that many others have missed out on. Hopefully it can keep doing that for a few years more."
Catagory = 3

